casebody.data:
WEED LUMBER CO. et al., Appellants and Cross-Appellees, v. James M. LEAVER, Jr., et al., Appellees and Cross-Appellants. No. 6936. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Aug. 15, 1932.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of counsel for appellees and cross-appellants, ordered appeal dismissed for failure of appellants to file record and docket cause; further ordered cross-appeal dismissed on motion of appellees.
